OL,5, A man has been found guilty of sending 
OL,6, racist messages to England football    
OL,7, manager Gareth Southgate.              
OL,9,FBrian Martin, 36, sent an              
OL,10,Fexpletive-laden email to Mr Southgate  
OL,11,Fon 4 June after England lost 1-0 to    
OL,12,FHungary, the Crown Prosecution Service 
OL,13,F(CPS) said.                            
OL,15,FMartin, from Selby, sent messages of "a
OL,16,Fracist nature", singling out black     
OL,17,Fplayers in the national team, according
OL,18,Fto the CPS.                            
OL,20,FHe is due to be sentenced on 13        
OL,21,FDecember.                              
